latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Want to bust a few weight-loss myths with me? Here’s me trying to pack the first 3 weeks of my nutrition course into a three-ish minute video! Quick takeaway: conscious eating > dieting! 

The internet has a plethora of information about hundreds of different diets and workout plans but it’s impossible to know which tips you can trust. I’ve lived with the same struggle in my own fitness journey. 

So, here I am with some weight-loss myths and tips grounded in science that I hope will help you improve your overall well-being ❤️

Was this video useful for you?  If you liked it please let me know in the comments because I’d love to make more content about women’s health and wellness!

latestIgtvVideos.title: How I take off my make up | Learn how to double cleanse
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It is a simple routine that I follow everytime I wear make up, whether it's for a shoot or a personal event.

1. @innisfreeindia cleansing oil 
This is one product I swear by. I have acne-prone skin but it doesn't give me any breakouts and is super gentle on my skin. I have been using it for over a year now.

2. @johnsonsbabyindia baby wipes

3. Cleanser @cetaphilme 
4. @thefaceshopindia_official 
Pomegranate and collagen volume lifting toner.

5. Moisturizer 
Apply sunscreen after, incase you're stepping out.

6. @vaselineindia  Works best for my chapped lips.
